License: MIT
Description: ================
        django-basicauth
        ================
        
        Basic auth utilities for Django.
        
        Requires
        ========
        
        Tested under...
        
        * Python
        
          * 3.6
        
        * Django
        
          * 1.8
          * 1.9
          * 1.10
          * 1.11
        
        Installation
        ============
        
        ::
        
            pip install django-basicauth
        
        
        Usage
        =====
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
            from basicauth.decorators import basic_auth_required
        
            @basic_auth_required
            def myview(request):
                ...
        
        or by a middleware.
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
            MIDDLEWARE_CLASSES = (
                'basicauth.middleware.BasicAuthMiddleware',
                ...
            )
        
        Settings
        ========
        
        * ``BASICAUTH_USERS`` (required): Dictionary including keys as username and values as passwords.
        * ``BASICAUTH_REALM``: realm string, default is "Secure resource".
        
        
        Changes
        =======
        
        0.2 (2016-03-31)
        ----------------
        
